Beijing’s Second Airport to Open in 2016, Shanghai Daily Reports

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-03-23T18:32:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/beijing-s-second-airport-to-open-in-2016-shanghai-daily-reports.html
Beijing Capital International
Airport Co. will begin work on a second airport in  China ’s
capital this year, with operations scheduled to start in 2016,
Shanghai Daily said, citing General Manager Zhang Guanghui.  The Bejing municipal government will invest in the second
airport, the English-language newspaper reported today. Zhang
declined to say how much money the city will provide.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  